&lt;li&gt;Experience in rapidly developing prototypes and iterating based on user feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate strong product intuition and experience leading initiatives spanning multiple teams and leveraging deep domain expertise to influence tech roadmap planning and execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have experience building and shipping products from scratch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading and influencing technical roadmaps for initiatives spanning multiple, highly interacting teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
