&lt;li&gt;Have a passion for working on side-projects, open source, or similar self-driven initiatives you’re proud of&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring energy and enthusiasm that inspires collaboration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
